{"kanda":6,"sarga":17,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"इत्युक्त्वापरुषंवाक्यंरावणंरावणानुजः ।आजगाममुहूर्तेनयत्ररामस्सलक्ष्मणः","trans":"Vibheeshana, having addressed Ravana in harsh language, reached Rama and Lakshmana in a short while.","words":[{"d":"रावणानुजः","m":"Ravana's brother, Vibheeshana"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"to Ravana"},{"d":"इति:","m":"thus"},{"d":"परुषम्","m":"in harsh"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"language"},{"d":"उक्त्वा:","m":"said"},{"d":"सलक्ष्मणः","m":"with Lakshmana"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"यत्र:","m":"there"},{"d":"मुहूर्तेन:","m":"in a short while"},{"d":"आजगाम:","m":"reached."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"तंमेरुशिखराकारंदीप्तामिवशतह्रदाम् ।गगनस्थंमहीस्थास्तेददृशुसर्ववानराः","trans":"All the Vanaras on the ground saw Vibheeshana who was like Mount Meru in form and shining like a brilliant lightning.","words":[{"d":"महीस्थाः","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"सर्ववानराः","m":"all Vanaras"},{"d":"मेरुशिखराकारम्","m":"like the Mount Meru in form"},{"d":"दीप्ताम्","m":"shining"},{"d":"शतह्रदाम् इव:","m":"like a brilliant lightning"},{"d":"गगनस्थम्","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"saw."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"येचाप्यनुचरास्तस्य चत्वारो भीमविक्रमा: ।तेsपि सर्वायुधोपेता भूषणैश्चापि भूषिता","trans":"His four companions of terrific prowess were also there with him. They were wearing all weapons and were adorned with excellent ornaments.","words":[{"d":"येच:","m":"these"},{"d":"अनुचरा:","m":"companions"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"चत्वार:","m":"four"},{"d":"भीमविक्रमा:","m":"or terrible prowess"},{"d":"ते","m":"s पि: they also"},{"d":"सर्वायुधोपेता:","m":"with all weapons"},{"d":"भूषणैश्चापि:","m":"with ornaments"},{"d":"भूषिता:","m":"adorned."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"स च मेघाचलप्रख्यो वज्रायुधसमप्रभः ।वरायुधधरो वीरो दिव्याभरणभूषितः","trans":"Vibheeshana looked like a mass of cloud, like someone who can cause thunderbolt, possessing excellent weapons and wonderful jewels.","words":[{"d":"स च","m":"And that Vibheeshana"},{"d":"मेघाचलप्रख्यो","m":"resembling a mass of cloud"},{"d":"वज्रायुधसमप्रभः","m":"the equal of the God who wields the thunderbolt"},{"d":"वीरो","m":"valiant man"},{"d":"वरायुधधरो","m":"wearing excellent weapons"},{"d":"दिव्याभरणभूषितः","m":"and adorned with wonderful jewels."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"तमात्मपञ्चमंदृष्टवासुग्रीवोवाहिनीपति: ।वानरैस्सहदुर्धर्षचिन्तयामासबुद्धिमान्","trans":"Wise Sugriva the Lord of the Vanara army, a formidable one along with Vanaras, started thinking on seeing Vibheeshana (the fifth one) besides four others.","words":[{"d":"दुर्धर्षः","m":"formidable one"},{"d":"बुद्धिमान्","m":"wise one"},{"d":"वाहिनीपति:","m":"Lord of the Vanara army"},{"d":"सुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"आत्मपञ्चमम्","m":"the fifth one besides four others"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"दृष्टवा:","m":"on seeing"},{"d":"वानरैःसह:","m":"along with Vanaras चिन्तयामास: started thinking."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"चिन्तयित्वामुहूर्तंतुवानरांस्तानुवाचह ।हनुमत्प्रमुखान्सर्वानिदंवचनमुत्तमम्","trans":"Reflecting for a while he addressed Hanuman and the other Vanara leaders in this way.","words":[{"d":"मुहूर्तम्","m":"for a while"},{"d":"चिन्तयित्वा:","m":"reflecting"},{"d":"हनुमत् प्रमुखान्","m":"leader Hanuman"},{"d":"तान्","m":"those"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"उत्तमम्","m":"best"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"these"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाचह:","m":"addressed."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"एषसर्वायुधोपेतश्चतुर्भिस्सहराक्षसैः ।राक्षसोऽभ्येतिपश्यध्वमस्मान्हन्तुंनसंशयः","trans":"Armed with all kinds of weapons this Rakshasa along with four Rakshasas are coming near to attack. You may see. There is no doubt.","words":[{"d":"सर्वायुधोपेतः","m":"armed with all kinds of weapons"},{"d":"एषःराक्षसः","m":"this Rakshasa"},{"d":"चतुर्भिराक्षसैःसह:","m":"along with four Rakshasas"},{"d":"अभ्येति:","m":"coming near"},{"d":"पश्यध्वम्","m":"you may see"},{"d":"अस्मान्","m":"us"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"to attack"},{"d":"संशयः","m":"doubt"},{"d":"नः","m":"no."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"सुग्रीवस्यवचश्रुत्वासर्वेतेवानरोत्तमाः ।