","trans":"\"This Rakshasa may be a spy who has found entry into our camp to create differences (among us). No doubt about it.\"","words":[{"d":"अयम्","m":"this one"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रस्य:","m":"Rakshasa king's"},{"d":"रावणस्य:","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"प्रणिधिः","m":"spy"},{"d":"भवेत्","m":"may be"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"अनुप्रविशय:","m":"having found a way to enter"},{"d":"अस्मासु:","m":"to our place"},{"d":"भेदम्","m":"difference"},{"d":"कूर्यात्","m":"to create"},{"d":"संशयः","m":"doubt"},{"d":"न:","m":"no."}]},{"v":23,"dev":"अथवास्वयमेवैषछिद्रमासाद्यबुद्धिमान् ।अनुप्रविश्यविश्वस्तेकदाचित्प्रहरेदपि","trans":"\"Or else if he is a wise one and knows our weak points, might have found a way and reached us. He may strike us if he is trusted.\"","words":[{"d":"अथवा:","m":"or else"},{"d":"बुद्धिमान्","m":"a wise one"},{"d":"एषः","m":"in this manner"},{"d":"स्वयमेव:","m":"on his own"},{"d":"छिद्रम्","m":"weak points"},{"d":"आसाद्य:","m":"having reached"},{"d":"अनुप्रविश्य:","m":"having found way"},{"d":"विश्वस्ते:","m":"if trusted"},{"d":"प्रहरेदपि:","m":"strike"},{"d":"कदाचित्","m":"perhaps."}]},{"v":24,"dev":"मित्राटवीबलंचैवमौलभृत्यबलंतथा ।सर्वमेतद्बलंग्राह्यंवर्जयित्वाद्विषद्बलम्","trans":"Army of friends or army from a jungle, so also an army brought up by a king for generations, army obtained on payment and all kinds of army except for enemies can be accepted.","words":[{"d":"मित्राटवीबलंचैव:","m":"army of friends or army from a jungle"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"so also"},{"d":"मौलभृत्यबलम्","m":"army brought up by the king for generations"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"that way"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"kinds of army"},{"d":"द्विषद्बलम्","m":"army that is obtained by payment"},{"d":"वर्जयित्वा:","m":"apart from (enemies)"},{"d":"ग्राह्यम्","m":"can be accepted."}]},{"v":25,"dev":"प्रकृत्याराक्षसेन्द्रस्यभ्राताऽमित्रस्यतेप्रभो: ।आगतश्चरिपोस्साक्षात्कथमस्मिन्हिविश्वसेत्","trans":"\"O king, by nature they are Rakshasas, and he is brother of the enemy. Evidently, he h