uspect"},{"d":"प्राप्तः","m":"one who appeared"},{"d":"शत्रुसैन्यम्","m":"enemy's army"},{"d":"शत्रुः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"अन्तरम्","m":"inside the hole"},{"d":"लब्ध्वा:","m":"having got access"},{"d":"उलूकः","m":"an owl"},{"d":"वायसानिव:","m":"like crows"},{"d":"निहन्यात्","m":"after killing."}]},{"v":29,"dev":"वध्यतामेषतीव्रेणदण्डेनसचिवैस्सह ।रावणस्यनृशंसस्यभ्राताह्येषविभीषणः","trans":"\"Let us kill this Vibheeshana by punishment along with his ministers as he is the brother of cruel Ravana (said Sugriva to Rama).\"","words":[{"d":"एषः","m":"that way"},{"d":"सचिवैः","m":"with ministers"},{"d":"तीव्रेण:","m":"severe"},{"d":"दण्डेन:","m":"by punishment"},{"d":"वध्यताम्","m":"will kill"},{"d":"एषःविभीषणः","m":"this Vibheeshana"},{"d":"नृशंसस्य:","m":"cruel"},{"d":"रावणस्यभ्राताहि:","m":"is Ravana's brother."}]},{"v":30,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वातुतंरामंसम्रब्धोवाहिनीपतिः ।वाक्यज्ञोवाक्यकुशलंततोमौनमुपागमत्","trans":"The chief of the army (Sugriva) who knew how to speak appropriately having submitted in that manner to Rama who was adept in expression remained silent.","words":[{"d":"वाहिनीपतिः","m":"the chief of the army"},{"d":"वाक्यज्ञः","m":"one who knows to speak"},{"d":"सम्रब्ध:","m":"well"},{"d":"वाक्यकुशलम्","m":"one who was adept in expression"},{"d":"तंरामम्","m":"him, to Rama"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"उक्त्वा:","m":"after having spoken"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"मौनम्","m":"silent"},{"d":"उपागमत्","m":"remained."}]},{"v":31,"dev":"सुग्रीवस्यतुतद्वाक्यंश्रुत्वारामोमहायशाः ।समीपस्थानुवाचेदंहनुमत्प्रमुखान्हरीन्","trans":"Rama of great fame having heard the words of Sugriva, addressed the Vanara army including the great Hanuman who stood close by.","words":[{"d":"महायशाः","m":"of great fame"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"सुग्रीवस्य:","m":"Sugriva's"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा:","m":"having heard"},{"d":"समीपस्थान्","m":"stood close by"},{"d":"हनुमत्प्रमुखान्","m":"including the great Hanuman"},{"d":"हरीन्","m":"to Vanaras"},{"d":"इदम