aspati"},{"d":"बृवन्","m":"proclaim"},{"d":"मतिश्रेष्ठम्","m":"highly intelligent"},{"d":"समर्थम्","m":"exceptionally capable"},{"d":"वदताम्","m":"in eloquence"},{"d":"वरम्","m":"foremost"},{"d":"भवन्तम्","m":"you"},{"d":"अतिशाययितुम्","m":"excellent"},{"d":"नशक्तः","m":"not possible."}]},{"v":52,"dev":"नवादान्नपिसङ्घर्षान्नाधिक्यान्नचकामतः ।वक्ष्यामिवचनंराजन्यथार्थंरामगौरवात्","trans":"\"O King Rama I am telling this to you truly not for the sake of argument, not for the sake of creating friction, or with a sense of superiority, or desire but out of respect.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"O king"},{"d":"राम:","m":"Rama"},{"d":"वादात्","m":"for the sake of argument"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"न:","m":"not"},{"d":"सङ्घर्षादपि:","m":"for the sake of creating friction"},{"d":"न:","m":"nor"},{"d":"आधिक्यात्","m":"with sense of superiority"},{"d":"न:","m":"nor"},{"d":"कामतःच:","m":"or even desire"},{"d":"न:","m":"nor"},{"d":"गौरवात्","m":"out of respect"},{"d":"यथार्थम्","m":"truth"},{"d":"वक्ष्यामि:","m":"telling you."}]},{"v":53,"dev":"अर्थानर्थनिमित्तंहियदुक्तंसचिवैस्तव ।तत्रदोषंप्रपश्यामिक्रियानह्युपपद्यते","trans":"\"Your counsellors have said that after judging good or bad qualities we should accept or reject Vibheeshana. I see a flaw in that statement as such action would not arise.\"","words":[{"d":"तव:","m":"your"},{"d":"सचिवैः","m":"counsellors"},{"d":"अर्थानर्थनिमित्तम्","m":"after judging good or bad qualities"},{"d":"यत्","m":"by what"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"has been said"},{"d":"तत्र:","m":"there"},{"d":"दोषम्","m":"fault"},{"d":"प्रपश्यामि:","m":"I see"},{"d":"क्रिया:","m":"action"},{"d":"नउपपद्यतेहि:","m":"not arise."}]},{"v":54,"dev":"ऋतेनियोगात्सामर्थ्यमवबोद्धुंनशक्यते ।सहसाविनियोगोहिदोषवान्प्रतिभातिमे","trans":"\"When entrusted with duty one's capability will be known. It is not possible to appoint him for duty inconsiderately without understanding (his capacity) as it will be faulty.\"","words":[{"d":"नियोगात् ऋते:","m":"only when entrusted with duty"},{"d":"सामर्थ्यम्","m":"capability"},{"d":"अवबोद्धुम्","m":"will be known"},{"d":"नशक्यते:","m":"not possible"},{"d":"सहसा:","m":"inconsiderately"},{"d":"विनियोगः","m":"appointment to a duty"},{"d":"दोषवान्","m":"will be faulty"},{"d":"मे:","m":"to me"},{"d":"प्रतिभाति:","m":"to understand."}]},{"v":55,"dev":"चारप्रणिहितंयुक्तंयदुक्तंसचिवैस्तव ।अर्थस्यासम्भवात्तत्रकारणंनोपयुज्यते","trans":"\"Your counsellors (Sarabha) have said that it is proper to know from the spies to ascertain about him. It has no meaning as it is not possible to do so (as he is near you). It does not serve the purpose.\"","words":[{"d":"तव:","m":"your"},{"d":"सचिवैः","m":"counsellors"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that way"},{"d":"चारप्रणिहितम्","m":"ascertain from the spies whether he is good or not"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"proper"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"has said"},{"d":"तत्र:","m":"then"},{"d":"अर्थस्य:","m":"has no meaning"},{"d":"असम्भवात्","m":"not possible to do"},{"d":"कारणम्","m":"reason"},{"d":"नोपयुज्यते:","m":"no purpose will be served by that."}]},{"v":56,"dev":"अदेशकालेसम्प्राप्तइत्ययंयद्विभीषणः ।विवक्षातत्रमेऽस्तीयंतांनिबोधयथामति","trans":"\"This Vibheeshana has come here without regard for place and time. I desire to speak what I feel in this regard.\"","words":[{"d":"अयंविभीषणः","m":"this Vibheeshana"},{"d":"आदेशकाले:","m":"without regard for place and time"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्तःइतियत्","m":"has come here"},{"d":"तत्र:","m":"hence"},{"d":"मे:","m":"my"},{"d":"यथामति:","m":"according to me"},{"d":"इयंविवक्षा:","m":"desire to speak this"},{"d":"अस्ति:","m":"will be"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"to it"},{"d":"निबोध:","m":"be considered."}]},{"v":57,"dev":"सएषदेश: कालश्चभवतीतियथातथा ।पुरुषात्पुरुषंप्राप्यतथादोषगुणावपि","trans":"\"It seems proper for him (Vibheeshana) to come here, considering place and time and so also considering that you are superior to him (Ravana) even if there are demerits in him and merits in you.\"","words":[{"d":"एषः","m":"this"},{"d":"इह:","m":"here"},{"d":"देश:","m":"place"},{"d":"कालश