e one"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"विशङ्केत:","m":"will become suspicious"},{"d":"तत्र:","m":"there"},{"d":"सुखागतम्","m":"come with relief"},{"d":"मित्रम्","m":"friend"},{"d":"मिथ्यापृष्टम् प्रदुष्येत:","m":"will appear as wicked one."}]},{"v":61,"dev":"अशक्यस्सहसाराजन्भावोबोद्धुंपरस्यवै ।अन्तस्स्वभावैर्गीतैस्तैर्नैपुण्यंपश्यतांभृशम्","trans":"\"O king It is not possible to know the intention (of an enemy) of others at once without excessive dexterity. It is to be known by his tone of words and description.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"O king अन्तस्स्वभावै: his intention"},{"d":"र्गीतै:","m":"tone of words स्तै: his"},{"d":"पश्यताम्","m":"to find out"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"excessive"},{"d":"नैपुण्यं:","m":"dexterity"},{"d":"परस्य:","m":"other's"},{"d":"भावः","m":"feelings"},{"d":"सहसा:","m":"at once"},{"d":"बोद्धुम्","m":"to know"},{"d":"अशक्यम्","m":"not possible."}]},{"v":62,"dev":"नत्वस्यब्रुवतोजातुलक्ष्यतेदुष्टभावता ।प्रसन्नंवदनंचापितस्मान्मेनास्तिसंशयः","trans":"\"Even when one is speaking, his malevolence is known. It does not seem so as his countenance is also pleasing. Therefore, I have no doubt (of him).\"","words":[{"d":"ब्रुवतः","m":"he is speaking"},{"d":"अस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"दुष्टभावता:","m":"malevolence"},{"d":"जातु:","m":"known"},{"d":"नलक्ष्यते:","m":"does not seem"},{"d":"वदनंचापि:","m":"even his countenance"},{"d":"प्रसन्नम्","m":"pleasing"},{"d":"तस्मात्","m":"therefore"},{"d":"मे:","m":"to me"},{"d":"संशयः","m":"suspicion"},{"d":"नास्ति:","m":"is not there."}]},{"v":63,"dev":"अशङ्कितमतिस्स्वस्थोनशठःपरिसर्पति ।नचास्यदुष्टावाक्चापितस्मान्नास्तीहसंशयः","trans":"\"One who is with deceitful feeling will not come without an expression of suspicion. He has come on his own and even his talk and looks are not suspicious to me.\"","words":[{"d":"शठः","m":"one with deceitful feeling"},{"d":"अशङ्कितमतिः","m":"without any expression of suspicion"},{"d":"स्वस्थः","m":"on his own"},{"d":"नपरिसर्पति:","m":"not going about"},{"d":"अस्य:","m":"his"},{"d":"वाक